dct_title_s: Radnor Breknok Cardigan et Caermarden quatuor australis Cambriæ comitatuum (B. Dehenbart, A Southwales) descriptio
dct_description_sm: Decorative border and cartouche, royal coat of arms and Seckford coat of arms.
Pictorial vignettes of ships, sea monster.
Appears in Saxton’s An atlas of England and Wales, London, 1579.
